          "description": "The Luna Hub is the web-based control interface for the Luna Engine. It provides real-time monitoring of Luna's consciousness state, conversation management, voice interaction controls, and developer debugging tools.",
          "technology_stack": [
            {"layer": "Framework", "technology": "React 18.2.0", "purpose": "Component-based UI"},
            {"layer": "Build Tool", "technology": "Vite", "purpose": "Fast HMR and bundling"},
